<p>Thanks Loz. When HTV left in the 1990s, it transformed again. Plays were workshopped, rehearsed, and even staged here – including a brilliant programme by schools called TYP – Theatre for Young People. That’s what I know this room as mostly – many hours practicing lines, dance numbers, quick costume changes...</p>
