:: 50_story-text-eng [nobr]
<<timed 0.1s>>
   <<append "#msgMount">>
<div class="quote">
  <p> “Theatr Clwyd, you know, has been my second home for over 20 years now. Every time I come here, I feel a strength in unity here. </p>

<p>And when Mags was with me up here, they treated Mags like one of the cast. Everybody knew Mags and she used to support all the cast as well, and everybody just loved seeing Mags there. So I want to thank everybody that’s gone out of their way to make me comfortable, knowing that Mags was in a safe environment and then able to do my job...</p>

<p>One of my lasting memories will always be, during a break of the  Robin Hood panto. I was dressed as Wonder Woman and, during the interval, there’s a picture of me pushing Mags into the toilet, me dressed as Wonder Woman and her in her wheelchair, you know. And we were both laughing, you know.. And that's what you get. Whatever problems you've got, they will look after you in Theatr Clwyd. They will go the extra mile. They really will."</p>
</div>
<br/>
  <</append>>
<</timed>>
<<timed 71s>>
   <<append "#msgMount">>
<p class="bold">That's magic.</p>
  <</append>>
